### v2.1.0: Supabase Auth Integration

Wired all auth pages to real Supabase authentication:

- [supabase.ts](file:///f:/Anuvaad/frontend/src/lib/supabase.ts) — Client singleton
- [auth-context.tsx](file:///f:/Anuvaad/frontend/src/lib/auth-context.tsx) — React context with `useAuth()` hook
- Dashboard route protection (redirects to `/signin` if unauthenticated)
- Real user email + Pro status in sidebar
- Sign-out with redirect

